    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah a CCB sounds better. i just feel like the \"creep\" happens so gradually that by the time i notice it, the sprint is already ruined. how do i actually catch it early? like is there a specific way to track the impact of these small additions before they snowball?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
